    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 Honestly, you have to see this beauty in person to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in showroom condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and has been pampered since day one. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. It\u2019s truly a rare find and totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
