    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece of preservation, presenting in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior paintwork retains a deep, mirror-like clarity, entirely devoid of the typical road rash, swirl marks, or imperfections found on most pre-owned examples. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the high-grade leather remains taut and supple, still carrying the faint scent of a new vehicle, while the carpets and headliner are immaculate. Every button, dial, and digital interface operates with the precision of the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook policy and exclusively serviced at authorized centers. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen a drop of rain. For the buyer who demands a vehicle indistinguishable from new, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a flawlessly maintained example of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
